channel.title: Alcher
channel.description: I have tried to find a script that just alchs yew longs, but I can't seem to be able to get one that works with the latest Scar and SRL 4. Anti-randoms is not needed, it only has to act human enough to click on the spell, then on the yew longs (in spot 14).
